  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Amplify Challenge No. 8: IDEO Mobile App for Rohingya Refugees</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project was designed to reach Rohingya women and CHWs through a mobile application to help inform them about menstrual regulation. Our questions were: &#x2022; How might we facilitate a pathway to menstrual regulation and contraception information and care for Rohingya women living in refugee camps in Bangladesh? &#x2022; What digital and/or physical tools does a community health worker need to counsel women and refer them to reproductive health and menstrual regulation services? &#x2022; What is the best way to provide information and referrals to Rohingya women who may not be literate?</narrative>
  </description>
